OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784679493
OL,3,CAustralian woman gives birth to rare
OL,4,Cidentical quadruplets
OL,6,FAn Australian woman has given birth to
OL,7,Frare identical quadruplets after an
OL,8,F"extremely high-risk" pregnancy.
OL,10,FBorn prematurely at 28 weeks and four
OL,11,Fdays, the four girls, Emily, Harriet,
OL,12,FAlexa and Catherine, were delivered by
OL,13,Fcaesarean section on July 14 at the
OL,14,FRoyal Brisbane and Women's Hospital.
OL,16,FThey are monozygotic quadruplets,
OL,17,Fmeaning they developed from a single
OL,18,Ffertilised egg that split into four
OL,19,Fembryos, which is extremely rare.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784679493
OL,3,CAustralian woman gives birth to rare
OL,4,Cidentical quadruplets
OL,6,FThe babies will remain in the
OL,7,Fhospital's neonatal intensive care
OL,8,Funit until they reach full term and
OL,9,Fare "currently doing extremely well",
OL,10,Fthe hospital said.
OL,12,FTheir mother, 34-year-old Jenitar
OL,13,FNa'amoana, and her husband Jortham,
OL,14,Fwho already have four children, were
OL,15,F"taken by immense surprise" when they
OL,16,Fdiscovered they were expecting
OL,17,Fquadruplets, it added.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@dO]wD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784679493
OL,3,CAustralian woman gives birth to rare
OL,4,Cidentical quadruplets
OL,6,FDr Alexa Bendall, who cared for Mrs
OL,7,FNa'amoana throughout her pregnancy,
OL,8,Festimated that identical quadruplets
OL,9,Foccur in around one in every 15
OL,10,Fmillion pregnancies.
OL,12,FThe maternal-fetal medicine specialist
OL,13,Fand obstetrician said the fact that
OL,14,Fthe babies also shared the same
OL,15,Fplacenta made the case even more
OL,16,Funusual.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784679493
OL,3,CAustralian woman gives birth to rare
OL,4,Cidentical quadruplets
OL,6,FShe said the pregnancy was considered
OL,7,Fextremely high risk, with Mrs
OL,8,FNa'amoana admitted to the hospital as
OL,9,Fan inpatient at 25 weeks so doctors
OL,10,Fcould closely monitor her and the
OL,11,Fbabies.
OL,13,F"We always said that if we could get
OL,14,Fher to 28 weeks, we would be doing
OL,15,Fwell," Bendall said.
OL,17,F"So the fact that we've got four
OL,18,Fbeautiful, healthy babies born at 28
OL,19,Fweeks and four days is incredible, and
OL,20,Fwe're very happy to be a part of it,"
OL,21,Fshe added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784679493
OL,3,CAustralian woman gives birth to rare
OL,4,Cidentical quadruplets
OL,6,F"Jenitar has taken everything in her
OL,7,Fstride from day one... she has somehow
OL,8,Fdodged every complication and risk for
OL,9,Fboth herself and her babies."
OL,11,FThe couple's other children are aged
OL,12,Fbetween one and ten, and Mrs Na'amoana
OL,13,Fhas launched an online fundraising
OL,14,Fcampaign to help the family buy a
OL,15,Fvehicle with enough seats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
