CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784679493
OL,3,CAustralian woman gives birth to rare
OL,4,Cidentical quadruplets
OL,6,FIn a message on the fundraiser, which
OL,7,Fhas already raised more than A$37,000
OL,8,F(#19,261), Mrs Na'amoana wrote: "Our
OL,9,Ffour precious miracles have arrived
OL,10,Fsafely, and while our hearts are
OL,11,Foverflowing with gratitude, the
OL,12,Freality of caring for four newborns at
OL,13,Fonce has brought challenges we never
OL,14,Fcould have imagined."
OL,16,FNaturally conceived quadruplets are
OL,17,Fextremely rare, with doctors
OL,18,Festimating the chances at around one
OL,19,Fin 700,000 births.
